_json.gridTitle: The Secret to Pretty Next Day Curls - Curly Tay
_json.description: August 2016 ➡️ September 2018 Holy #transformationtuesday I haven't looked back at pics from this long ago in forever! In the first pic, I was dying my hair every 6ish weeks with quite literally the cheapest hair dye that I could find at Walmart. My hair had always been wavy, but the longer I used that hair dye, the straighter I noticed my hair becoming. This pic was actually right before I had all of the black stripped out so that I could embrace my natural color and start working toward ...
